high_descs: Turn and go to the couch with the round yellow plaid pillow on it.
Pick up the remote that is to the right of the yellow plaid pillow.
Go to the chair that is to the right of the tv.
Place the remote on the front center of the chair.
Go to the couch where the round plaid pillow is.
Pick up the remote that is to the left of the pillow on the couch.
Turn around and go to the tv.  Turn right at the tv. Go to the chair and face it on the side.
Place the remote right behind the remote that is already on the cushion.
Turn around and walk to the couch with the yellow cushion on it.
Pick up the remote to the right side of the pillow.
Turn around and walk to the left side of the ottoman and face the left side of the chair.
Place the remote on the chair.
Turn right and veer left to the couch, this time to the left of the cushion.
Pick up the remote.
Turn around and walk back to the far side of the chair.
Place the remote in back of and to the left of the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Place two remotes on a chair.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the couch.
Pick up the remote that is to the right of the yellow pillow on the couch.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the chair.
Put the remote on the seat of the chair.
Turn right and walk back over to the couch.
Pick up the remote off of the seat of the couch.
Turn around and walk towards the television, then hang a right and walk over to the chair.
Put the remote on the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to a chair seat.
